# Rules for doing perceptual processing in a substate if desired

problem-space.perception
 attend-to-all-perception << yes no >>
   If yes, for any top-state.perception-monitor.changes.change
     it will propose attend-to-perception for that

 attend-to-object <obj-handle>
   Given a propose object handle, this will propose attend-to-perception
   For any top-state.perception-monitor.changes.change involving that object

 attend-to-robot << yes no >>
   If yes, it will propose attend-to-perception 
     for any top-state.perception-monitor.changes.change involving the robot
